  <main class="px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:flex-auto lg:px-0">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl space-y-16 sm:space-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">Portal Settings</h2>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-500">Configure your campsite portal settings and integrations.</p>

        <div class="mt-6 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 bg-yellow-50 p-4">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.485 2.495c.673-1.167 2.357-1.167 3.03 0l6.28 10.875c.673 1.167-.17 2.625-1.516 2.625H3.72c-1.347 0-2.189-1.458-1.515-2.625L8.485 2.495zM10 5a.75.75 0 01.75.75v3.5a.75.75 0 01-1.5 0v-3.5A.75.75 0 0110 5zm0 9a1 1 0 100-2 1 1 0 000 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
                <strong class="font-medium">Coming Soon:</strong>
                Portal configuration features are currently under development. You'll be able to customize your portal settings, integrations, and guest experiences here.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium leading-6 text-gray-900">Planned Features</h3>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li>Custom portal branding and themes</li>
              <li>Guest communication preferences</li>
              <li>Booking widget configuration</li>
              <li>Integration with external services</li>
              <li>Portal access controls</li>
              <li>Guest self-service options</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>
